{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"70207b1755","title":"毛泽东对陶铸关于广西剿匪工作报告的批语和复电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ae41b388c4","index":0,"year":1951,"month":1,"day":7,"articleId":"70207b1755"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dbcf15bd08","name":"陶铸","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fdbe183bee","type":"title","text":"毛泽东对陶铸关于广西剿匪工作报告的批语和复电","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"70207b1755"},{"id":"c53799b1a4","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"70207b1755"},{"id":"0d7238ef5b","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"70207b1755"},{"id":"6a728e7680","type":"appellation","text":"陈饶、邓贺、习张各同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"70207b1755"},{"id":"c7451f2aeb","type":"paragraph","text":"兹将陶铸同志十二月卅一日电发给你们参考，并请你们转发所属剿匪尚处严重情况的地方和军队阅看。我们认为广西最近时期的经验是很好的，值得研究。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"70207b1755"},{"id":"da2fc1a2d7","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东一月七日","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"70207b1755"},{"id":"f6ed6216a3","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"70207b1755"},{"id":"47e3bedc25","type":"appellation","text":"陶铸同志并告广西省委，中南局：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"70207b1755"},{"id":"2f61f472f6","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）十一月卅一日关于广西剿匪工作顺利进展的报告已阅悉，甚好甚慰，已转华东西南西北三区参考。（二）既然两大重点区土匪可以在三月以前剿清，请考虑进剿西北部土匪是否可以只要二十一兵团去而不要四十五军去，以便将四十五军从剿匪中解放出来于三月间即开至梧州地区整训待命，准备应付广东方面的万一情况。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"70207b1755"},{"id":"bd6d37820e","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东一月九日","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz"